Product's Title: nylon and suede running sneakers with durable sole
Description: Golden Goose Running Sole sneakers with a used effect, made of ripstop nylon with suede inserts, smooth leather side star and logoed and glittery spoiler. Gold logo print on the side, fabric label on the tongue and closure with initials. Leather and sponge interior with removable insole, rubber sole with contrasting tread.

Hogan Skyscraper sneakers, made of smooth leather and featuring clean lines and an urban chic vibe. The upper is inspired by basketball shoes with a perforated toe, laminated lettering logo on the outer side, and embossed logo on the tongue. The interior is lined with padded fabric and comes with a 5mm memory foam removable insole, while the platform rubber sole boasts an embossed logo on the back.

The Amiri Classic Low Sneakers feature a leather and mesh upper with star-shaped perforations and contrasting rubber logo lettering on the sides. They have a front lace-up closure, monogram on the tongue, fabric lining with removable insole, and a rubber sole.

Golden Goose Ball Star sneakers in used-effect leather with glittered iconic suede side star and heel tab. Perforated toe and lettering logo on tongue, and "SNEAKERS" print on the heel. Terry lining with removable leather insole, rubber sole with contrasting base.
